            <title>[KAFKA-591] Add test cases to test log size retention and more</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-591</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add test cases to test the followings:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Log Size Retention&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. Replica Factor &amp;lt; no. of brokers in a cluster&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. Multiple instances of Migration Tool&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4. Multiple instances of Mirror Maker&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;5. Set &quot;log.index.interval.bytes&quot; to be slightly smaller than message size to force the indexing to be performed for each message&lt;/p&gt;</description>
