                            <comment id="13490804" author="jfung" created="Mon, 5 Nov 2012 18:36:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Uploaded kafka-591-v1.patch with the following changes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. Added Log Size Retention (cases 4001 ~ 4008, 4011 ~ 4018)&lt;br/&gt;
2. Replica Factor &amp;lt; no. of brokers in a cluster (cases 4011 ~ 4018)&lt;br/&gt;
3. Multiple instances of Migration Tool (cases 9003 ~ 9006)&lt;br/&gt;
4. Multiple instances of Mirror Maker (cases 5003 ~ 5006)&lt;br/&gt;
5. Set &quot;log.index.interval.bytes&quot; to be slightly smaller than message size to force the indexing to be performed for each message (cases 0124 ~ 0127)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13493781" author="jfung" created="Fri, 9 Nov 2012 07:00:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Uploaded kafka-591-v2.patch with the following changes:&lt;/p&gt;

